name: Perfect Summer Scent
description: After 300 post-apocalyptic summers, portraits of human life are not as rusty and dusty as you might imagine. In fact, the world has become 9000 times better, natural, & flowery. Every human mutates into a half-animal with their special bloodline only every summer. Here is a post-apocalyptic human Jzaka and his son Ahndy are celebrating the summer
